728350f-a.title: Richmond: Arden Avenue - Amboy Road
728350f-a.text:
Arden Ave. (directly behind house, telephone poles thereon),
adjoining the N.E. corner of Amboy Road, showing the Bovaniser
house occupying that site. The house belonged to J. Dempsey in 1874
(Beers' map). The view is northwestward.
Amril 30, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
